  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped shio-cured beef and cook until lightly browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the ground cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced beets and cook until tender, about 20-25 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot.",
    "Serve with crusty bread or over rice."
